Package: poissontris
Type: Package
Title: poissontris - a shiny game
Version: 0.0-2
Date: 2017-07-07
Author: Jason Waddell 
Maintainer: Jason Waddell <jason.waddell@openanalytics.eu>
Description: A shiny package for running the Poissontris game. Number of blocks in a piece are sampled from the poisson distribution. As you clear lines, Lambda increases. Controller use and high-score tracking supported
License: Software for Internal Use at Open Analytics NV
Depends: oaColors, oaPlots, htmltools, svglite, pryr, shiny